<h2>Welcome</h2>
<p>
Welcome to the Soybean and Corn Advisor.  Our mission is to provide our readers with up-to-date information about soybean and corn production.  We provide crop analysis that you cannot find anywhere else.  In addition to articles that deal primarily with soybean and corn production, you will find detailed information about crops such as wheat, cotton and sugarcane as well as alcohol and biodiesel production.  The Soybean And Corn Advisor is your source for analysis of crop conditions in both North and South America.  
</p>